# Syncthing — sync port (TCP+UDP 22000) and local discovery (UDP 21027)
add rule inet filter input tcp dport 22000 ct state new accept comment "allow Syncthing sync TCP"
add rule inet filter input udp dport 22000 ct state new accept comment "allow Syncthing sync UDP"
add rule inet filter input udp dport 21027 ct state new accept comment "allow Syncthing local discovery"
